{
  "spec": "# Component Specification: Add / Edit Bookmark\n\n**QuickMarks — Screen 2**\n**Spec Version:** 1.0\n**Status:** Ready for Implementation\n\n---\n\n## 1. Component Tree\n\n```\nAddEditBookmarkPage\n├── PageHeader\n│   ├── BackNavigation\n│   │   ├── BackIcon (← arrow)\n│   │   └── BackLabel (\"Bookmarks\")\n│   └── PageTitle (\"Add Bookmark\" | \"Edit Bookmark\")\n│\n├── DirtyWarningBar [CONDITIONAL: isDirty && cancelRequested]\n│   ├── WarningIcon\n│   ├── WarningText (\"You have unsaved changes\")\n│   └── WarningActions\n│       ├── DiscardButton (\"Discard\")\n│       └── KeepEditingButton (\"Keep editing\")\n│\n├── FormContainer [CONDITIONAL: !isNotFound]\n│   ├── FormField [title]\n│   │   ├── FieldLabel (\"Title\" + RequiredIndicator)\n│   │   ├── TextInput [id=\"title\"]\n│   │   └── FieldError [id=\"title-error\"] [CONDITIONAL: touched && invalid]\n│   │\n│   ├── FormField [url]\n│   │   ├── FieldLabel (\"URL\" + RequiredIndicator)\n│   │   ├── TextInput [id=\"url\", type=\"url\"]\n│   │   └── FieldError [id=\"url-error\"] [CONDITIONAL: touched && invalid]\n│   │\n│   ├── FormField [tags]\n│   │   ├── FieldLabel (\"Tags\" + OptionalIndicator)\n│   │   ├── TagInputField\n│   │   │   ├── TagChipStrip\n│   │   │   │   └── TagChip [×N, one per committed tag]\n│   │   │   │       ├── TagLabel\n│   │   │   │       └── RemoveButton (\"×\")\n│   │   │   └── TagTextInput [id=\"tags-input\"]\n│   │   ├── TagHelperText [id=\"tags-helper\"] (persistent)\n│   │   └── FieldError [id=\"tags-error\"] [CONDITIONAL: touched && invalid]\n│   │\n│   ├── FormField [notes]\n│   │   ├── FieldLabel (\"Notes\" + OptionalIndicator)\n│   │   ├── Textarea [id=\"notes\"]\n│   │   ├── CharCounter [id=\"notes-counter\"] (live, always visible)\n│   │   └── FieldError [id=\"notes-error\"] [CONDITIONAL: touched && invalid]\n│   │\n│   └── FormActions\n│       ├── SaveButton (\"Save Bookmark\" | \"Update Bookmark\") [type=\"submit\"]\n│       └── CancelButton (\"Cancel\") [type=\"button\"]\n│\n└── NotFoundState [CONDITIONAL: isNotFound]\n    ├── NotFoundText (\"Bookmark not found\")\n    └── GoBackLink (\"← Go back\")\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Component Specifications\n\n### 2.1 `AddEditBookmarkPage`\n\n**Role:** Root layout container. Owns form state, dirty detection, validation state machine, and routing logic.\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Background | `background-primary` → `#FAFAF7` |\n| Layout | Flex column, align-items: center |\n| Min-height | 100vh |\n| Padding (mobile) | `16px` horizontal, `24px` vertical |\n| Padding (tablet+) | `32px` horizontal, `48px` vertical |\n\n**State owned at this level:**\n\n```\nformValues: { title, url, tags[], notes }\ninitialValues: snapshot at mount (for dirty detection)\ntouchedFields: Set<fieldName>\nfieldErrors: Map<fieldName, errorMessage | null>\nisDirty: boolean (derived: formValues !== initialValues)\ncancelRequested: boolean\nisSubmitting: boolean\nisNotFound: boolean (edit mode only)\nmode: \"add\" | \"edit\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2.2 `PageHeader`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex row, align-items: center, gap: `16px` |\n| Width | 100%, max-width: `480px` |\n| Margin-bottom | `24px` |\n\n#### `BackNavigation`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<a>` or `<button>` with router link |\n| Layout | Flex row, align-items: center, gap: `8px` |\n| Token: text color | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` |\n| Token: hover color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Font | `label` → Source Sans 3, 12px/500 |\n| Min tap target | 44×44px |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px |\n| Aria-label | \"Back to Bookmarks\" |\n\n#### `PageTitle`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<h1>` |\n| Token: font | `heading-2` → Sora, 24px/700 |\n| Token: color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Content (add) | \"Add Bookmark\" |\n| Content (edit) | \"Edit Bookmark\" |\n\n---\n\n### 2.3 `DirtyWarningBar`\n\n**Trigger:** Visible when `isDirty === true && cancelRequested === true`.\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<div role=\"alert\">` |\n| Layout | Flex row, align-items: center, gap: `12px`, flex-wrap: wrap |\n| Width | 100%, max-width: `480px` |\n| Padding | `12px 16px` |\n| Token: background | `warning` → `marigold-400` → `#E8A838` |\n| Token: text color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` (verify ≥ 4.5:1 on marigold-400) |\n| Border-radius | `small` → `8px` |\n| Margin-bottom | `24px` |\n| Motion: appear | Fade-in + slide-down `normal` (200ms) `ease-out`; instant when `prefers-reduced-motion` |\n| ARIA | `role=\"alert\"` — announces once on appearance |\n\n#### `WarningIcon`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Icon | Warning/caution filled, rounded style |\n| Size | 20×20px |\n| Color | `charcoal-900` |\n| Aria-hidden | `true` |\n\n#### `WarningText`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Font | `body` → Source Sans 3, 14px/400 |\n| Color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Flex | `1` (fills available space) |\n| Content | \"You have unsaved changes\" |\n\n#### `DiscardButton`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<button type=\"button\">` |\n| Font | `body` weight 500 → Source Sans 3, 14px/500 |\n| Color | `error` → `terracotta-400` → `#D4735A` |\n| Background | Transparent |\n| Border | None |\n| Min tap target | 44×44px |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px |\n| On click | Navigate to `/` (discard) |\n\n#### `KeepEditingButton`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<button type=\"button\">` |\n| Font | `body` weight 500 → Source Sans 3, 14px/500 |\n| Color | `cta-primary` → `sage-500` → `#5C8A6E` |\n| Background | Transparent |\n| Border | None |\n| Min tap target | 44×44px |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px |\n| Initial focus | Receives focus when bar appears |\n| On click | `cancelRequested = false`; return focus to last active field |\n\n---\n\n### 2.4 `FormContainer`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<form>` |\n| Width | 100%, max-width: `480px` |\n| Token: background | `surface-primary` → `linen-100` → `#F4F1EB` |\n| Token: shadow | `elevation.level-1` → `0 1px 4px rgba(28,25,23,0.07), 0 1px 2px rgba(28,25,23,0.05)` |\n| Border-radius | `medium` → `12px` |\n| Padding | `32px` |\n| Layout | Flex column, gap: `24px` (between `FormField` siblings) |\n| Novalidate | `true` (suppress browser-native validation UI) |\n\n---\n\n### 2.5 `FormField` (Wrapper — composable)\n\nShared wrapper used for all four fields. Encapsulates label, input slot, helper text slot, and error slot.\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex column, gap: `4px` |\n| Gap: label → input | `8px` (label margin-bottom or gap override) |\n| Gap: input → error/helper | `4px` |\n\n#### `FieldLabel`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<label for=\"[fieldId]\">` |\n| Font | `label` → Source Sans 3, 12px/500 |\n| Color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Display | Flex row, align-items: center, gap: `4px` |\n\n#### `RequiredIndicator`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<span aria-hidden=\"true\">` + `<span class=\"sr-only\">` \"(required)\" |\n| Visual | \"(Required)\" text in `text-secondary` color, or asterisk `*` with visually-hidden text |\n| Font | `label` → 12px/500 |\n| Color | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` |\n\n> **Implementation note:** Use visible text \"(Required)\" rather than asterisk-only. `aria-required=\"true\"` on the input is the machine-readable signal.\n\n#### `OptionalIndicator`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<span>` |\n| Content | \"(Optional)\" |\n| Font | `label` → 12px/500, italic permitted |\n| Color | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` |\n\n#### `FieldError`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<span id=\"[field]-error\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"assertive\">` |\n| Font | `small` → Source Sans 3, 11px/400 |\n| Color | `error` → `terracotta-400` (`#D4735A`); fallback `terracotta-600` (`#B85A41`) if contrast < 4.5:1 on `linen-50` |\n| Visibility | Hidden (height: 0, aria-hidden) when no error; revealed when error present |\n| Motion | Fade-in `fast` (100ms); instant when `prefers-reduced-motion` |\n| Icon | Optional: small error icon, aria-hidden |\n\n> **Contrast note:** `terracotta-400` (#D4735A) on `linen-50` (#FAFAF7) → compute at build time. If below 4.5:1, use `terracotta-600` (#B85A41) for all error text.\n\n---\n\n### 2.6 `TextInput` (Title & URL fields)\n\n| Property | Specification |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<input>` |\n| Token: background | `surface-input` → `linen-50` → `#FAFAF7` |\n| Token: border default | `border-default` → `linen-200` → `#E8E2D9`, 1px solid |\n| Token: border focus | `border-focus` → `sage-500` → `#5C8A6E`, 2px solid |\n| Token: border error | `border-error` → `terracotta-400`, 2px solid |\n| Border-radius | `small` → `8px` |\n| Padding | `12px 16px` |\n| Font | `body` → Source Sans 3, 14px/400 |\n| Color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Width | 100% |\n| Height | `44px` minimum (touch target compliance) |\n| Transition | border-color `fast` (100ms) `ease-out`; suppressed at `prefers-reduced-motion` |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px (via outline, not box-shadow) |\n| aria-required | `true` (both fields) |\n| aria-invalid | `\"true\"` when field has error, `\"false\"` otherwise |\n| aria-describedby | `\"[field]-error\"` always; append `\" [field]-helper\"` when helper present |\n\n**Title-specific:**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| id | `title` |\n| type | `text` |\n| maxlength | `120` |\n| autocomplete | `off` |\n| autofocus | On page load (both add and edit modes) |\n\n**URL-specific:**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| id | `url` |\n| type | `url` |\n| placeholder | `https://example.com` |\n| autocomplete | `url` |\n| Placeholder color | `charcoal-500` (meets 4.5:1 on `linen-50`) |\n\n---\n\n### 2.7 `TagInputField`\n\nComposite component. Owns internal tag list state and token commit logic.\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex column, gap: `8px` |\n| Border | 1px solid `border-default`; 2px `border-focus` when TagTextInput is focused; 2px `border-error` when error |\n| Border-radius | `small` → `8px` |\n| Padding | `8px 12px` |\n| Background | `surface-input` → `linen-50` |\n| Focus-within border | 2px solid `sage-500` |\n\n#### `TagChipStrip`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex row, flex-wrap: wrap, gap: `8px` |\n| Min-height | `0` (collapses when no chips) |\n| Margin-bottom | `4px` when chips present |\n\n#### `TagChip`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex row, align-items: center, gap: `6px` |\n| Background | `cta-primary` → `sage-500` |\n| Color | `text-on-cta` → `linen-50` |\n| Font | `label` → Source Sans 3, 12px/500 |\n| Padding | `4px 10px` |\n| Border-radius | `pill` → `9999px` |\n| Max-width | `160px`, text truncated with ellipsis |\n\n##### `RemoveButton` (on TagChip)\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<button type=\"button\">` |\n| Content | `×` (Unicode U+00D7) |\n| Aria-label | `\"Remove tag [tagName]\"` |\n| Min tap target | 44×44px (expanded via padding/negative margin) |\n| Background | Transparent |\n| Color | `text-on-cta` → `linen-50` |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `linen-50` (inverted, visible on sage background) |\n| On click | Remove tag from list, re-validate count |\n| On Backspace/Delete (focused) | Same as click |\n\n#### `TagTextInput`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<input type=\"text\">` |\n| id | `tags-input` |\n| Placeholder | \"Add a tag…\" |\n| Background | Transparent |\n| Border | None (border lives on `TagInputField` container) |\n| Font | `body` → Source Sans 3, 14px/400 |\n| Color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Width | 100%, min-width: `120px` |\n| aria-describedby | `\"tags-helper tags-error\"` |\n| aria-label | \"Tag input — press comma or Enter to add\" |\n| On keydown comma / Enter | Tokenize current value → validate → commit or show error |\n| On blur | Tokenize trailing value if non-empty |\n\n#### `TagHelperText`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| id | `tags-helper` |\n| Element | `<span>` |\n| Font | `small` → Source Sans 3, 11px/400 |\n| Color | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` |\n| Visibility | Always visible |\n| Content | \"Separate tags with commas. Letters, numbers, and hyphens only. Max 5 tags.\" |\n\n---\n\n### 2.8 `Textarea` (Notes)\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<textarea>` |\n| id | `notes` |\n| Token: background | `surface-input` → `linen-50` |\n| Token: border default | `border-default`, 1px solid |\n| Token: border focus | `border-focus` → `sage-500`, 2px solid |\n| Token: border error | `border-error` → `terracotta-400`, 2px solid |\n| Border-radius | `small` → `8px` |\n| Padding | `12px 16px` |\n| Font | `body` → Source Sans 3, 14px/400 |\n| Color | `text-primary` → `charcoal-900` |\n| Width | 100% |\n| Min-height | `80px` (≈ 3 lines) |\n| Resize | `vertical` only |\n| aria-required | `false` |\n| aria-invalid | `\"true\"` when error |\n| aria-describedby | `\"notes-counter notes-error\"` |\n| autocomplete | `off` |\n\n#### `CharCounter`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| id | `notes-counter` |\n| Element | `<span aria-live=\"polite\">` |\n| Layout | Align right (text-align: end) |\n| Font | `small` → Source Sans 3, 11px/400 |\n| Color default | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` (0–260 chars) |\n| Color warning | `warning` → `marigold-400` (261–279 chars) — verify contrast |\n| Color error | `error` → `terracotta-400` (280+ chars) |\n| Content | `{currentLength} / 280` |\n| Aria-label | `\"{currentLength} of 280 characters used\"` |\n| Update timing | On every `input` event (live) |\n\n---\n\n### 2.9 `FormActions`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Layout | Flex row, gap: `12px`, justify-content: flex-start |\n| Margin-top | `8px` (within form gap of `24px` provides total `32px` from last field) |\n| Width | 100% |\n\n#### `SaveButton`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<button type=\"submit\">` |\n| Content (add) | \"Save Bookmark\" |\n| Content (edit) | \"Update Bookmark\" |\n| Token: background | `cta-primary` → `sage-500` → `#5C8A6E` |\n| Token: background hover | `cta-hover` → `sage-600` → `#4A7259` |\n| Token: text | `text-on-cta` → `linen-50` |\n| Font | Sora, 15px/500 |\n| Padding | `12px 24px` |\n| Min-height | `44px` |\n| Border-radius | `pill` → `9999px` |\n| Border | None |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px |\n| Disabled state | Background: `cta-primary` at `opacity.disabled` (0.38); `disabled` attribute set during `isSubmitting` |\n| Motion: hover | background-color transition `fast` (100ms) `ease-out` |\n| aria-disabled | Reflects `isSubmitting` |\n\n#### `CancelButton`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Element | `<button type=\"button\">` |\n| Content | \"Cancel\" |\n| Background | Transparent |\n| Token: text | `text-secondary` → `charcoal-500` |\n| Token: border | `border-default` → `linen-200`, 1px solid |\n| Font | Sora, 15px/500 |\n| Padding | `12px 24px` |\n| Min-height | `44px` |\n| Border-radius | `pill` → `9999px` |\n| Focus ring | 2px solid `sage-500`, offset 2px |\n| Hover | border-color → `charcoal-300`; text → `text-primary` |\n| On click (clean form) | Navigate to `/` immediately |\n| On click (dirty form) | Set `cancelRequested = true`, show DirtyWarningBar, focus KeepEditingButton |\n\n---\n\n### 2.10 `NotFoundState`\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Render condition | `isNotFound === true` (replaces FormContainer) |\n| Layout | Flex column, align-items: center, gap: `16px`, padding: `32px` |\n| Token: background | `surface-primary` → `linen-100` |\n| Border-radius | `medium` → `12px` |\n| Shadow | `elevation.level-1` |\n| Width | 100%, max-width: `480px` |\n\n| Child | Specification |\n|---|---|\n| `NotFoundText` | `<p>` · `body` · `text-primary` · \"Bookmark not found.\" |\n| `GoBackLink` | `<a>` or `<button>` → navigate `/` · \"← Go back\" · `cta-primary` color · `label` font · min 44×44px |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Layout Rules\n\n### 3.1 Page-Level Centering\n\n```\nAddEditBookmarkPage\n  display: flex\n  flex-direction: column\n  align-items: center          ← horizontal centering\n  min-height: 100vh\n  padding: [24px 16px] mobile / [48px 32px] tablet+\n  background: background-primary\n```\n\n```\nAll direct children (PageHeader, DirtyWarningBar, FormContainer, NotFoundState):\n  width: 100%\n  max-width: 480px             ← the single-column max-width constraint\n```\n\n### 3.2 Vertical Spacing Stack\n\n```\nPageHeader\n  ↕ margin-bottom: 24px\nDirtyWarningBar (conditional)\n  ↕ margin-bottom: 24px (when visible)\nFormContainer\n  ↕ internal padding: 32px\n  ↕ between FormFields: 24px (flex gap)\n  ↕ between label and input: 8px\n  ↕ between input and error/helper: 4px\n  ↕ before FormActions: 32px total (8px explicit + 24px gap = 32px from last field)\n  ↕ between Save and Cancel: 12px (flex gap on FormActions)\n```\n\n### 3.3 Field-Internal Structure\n\n```\nFormField\n├── FieldLabel          [margin-bottom: 8px]\n├── Input/Textarea      [full-width]\n├── HelperText          [margin-top: 4px] (tags only, always visible)\n└── FieldError          [margin-top: 4px, conditional]\n```\n\n### 3.4 Tab Order (Sequential)\n\n```\n1. BackNavigation\n2. Title TextInput\n3. URL TextInput\n4. TagChip[0] RemoveButton ... TagChip[N] RemoveButton (when chips present)\n5. TagTextInput\n6. Notes Textarea\n7. SaveButton\n8. CancelButton\n9. DirtyWarningBar: KeepEditingButton → DiscardButton (when bar visible)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Token Bindings\n\n### 4.1 Color Bindings\n\n| Component / State | Token | Resolved Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page background | `background-primary` | `#FAFAF7` |\n| Form card background | `surface-primary` | `#F4F1EB` |\n| Input background | `surface-input` | `#FAFAF7` |\n| Input border (default) | `border-default` | `#E8E2D9` |\n| Input border (focus) | `border-focus` | `#5C8A6E` |\n| Input border (error) | `border-error` | `#D4735A` |\n| Input text | `text-primary` | `#1C1917` |\n| Placeholder text | `text-secondary` | `#78716C` |\n| Label text | `text-primary` | `#1C1917` |\n| Helper / secondary text | `text-secondary` | `#78716C` |\n| Error message text | `error` (→ fallback `terracotta-600`) | `#D4735A` / `#B85A41` |\n| Save button bg | `cta-primary` | `#5C8A6E` |\n| Save button bg (hover) | `cta-hover` | `#4A7259` |\n| Save button text | `text-on-cta` | `#FAFAF7` |\n| Cancel button text | `text-secondary` | `#78716C` |\n| Cancel button border | `border-default` | `#E8E2D9` |\n| Tag chip background | `cta-primary` | `#5C8A6E` |\n| Tag chip text | `text-on-cta` | `#FAFAF7` |\n| Discard button text | `error` | `#D4735A` |\n| Keep editing text | `cta-primary` | `#5C8A6E` |\n| Warning bar background | `warning` | `#E8A838` |\n| Warning bar text | `text-primary` | `#1C1917` |\n| Char counter (default) | `text-secondary` | `#78716C` |\n| Char counter (near limit) | `warning` | `#E8A838` |\n| Char counter (over limit) | `error` | `#D4735A` |\n| Focus ring | `cta-primary` | `#5C8A6E`, 2px, offset 2px |\n\n### 4.2 Typography Bindings\n\n| Component | Token | Resolved |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page title `<h1>` | `heading-2` | Sora 24px/700, lh 1.25 |\n| Field labels | `label` | Source Sans 3 12px/500, lh 1.4 |\n| Input / textarea text | `body` | Source Sans 3 14px/400, lh 1.5 |\n| Helper text | `small` | Source Sans 3 11px/400, lh 1.4 |\n| Error messages | `small` | Source Sans 3 11px/400, lh 1.4 |\n| Char counter | `small` | Source Sans 3 11px/400, lh 1.4 |\n| Button labels | Sora 15px/500 | (display family, mid-scale — between `label` and `body`) |\n| Back navigation | `label` | Source Sans 3 12px/500 |\n| Warning bar text | `body` | Source Sans 3 14px/400 |\n| Not-found text | `body` | Source Sans 3 14px/400 |\n\n### 4.3 Spacing Bindings\n\n| Usage | Token Scale Value |\n|---|---|\n| Form container padding | `32` |\n| Between FormFields (gap) | `24` |\n| Label → input gap | `8` |\n| Input → error/helper gap | `4` |\n| FormActions margin-top | `8` (+ 24 gap = 32 from last field) |\n| Save → Cancel gap | `12` |\n| DirtyWarningBar margin-bottom | `24` |\n| PageHeader margin-bottom | `24` |\n| Warning bar padding | `12` vertical / `16` horizontal |\n| Tag chip gap (in strip) | `8` |\n| Back icon → back label gap | `8` |\n\n### 4.4 Border Radius Bindings\n\n| Element | Token | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| TextInput, Textarea, TagInputField | `small` | 8px |\n| FormContainer card | `medium` | 12px |\n| TagChip | `pill` | 9999px |\n| SaveButton, CancelButton | `pill` | 9999px |\n| DirtyWarningBar | `small` | 8px |\n| NotFoundState | `medium` | 12px |\n\n### 4.5 Elevation Bindings\n\n| Element | Token | Shadow |\n|---|---|---|\n| FormContainer | `elevation.level-1` | `0 1px 4px rgba(28,25,23,0.07), 0 1px 2px rgba(28,25,23,0.05)` |\n| NotFoundState | `elevation.level-1` | same |\n| All other elements | `elevation.level-0` | none |\n\n### 4.6 Motion Bindings\n\n| Interaction | Duration Token | Easing | Reduced-motion override |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Input border-color on focus/error | `fast` (100ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n| Error message appear | `fast` (100ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n| DirtyWarningBar appear | `normal` (200ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n| Button hover background | `fast` (100ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n| Tag chip appear | `fast` (100ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n| Char counter color shift | `fast` (100ms) | `ease-out` | instant |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Responsive Breakpoints\n\n### 5.1 Breakpoint Definitions\n\n| Breakpoint | Token Value | Range |\n|---|---|---|\n| `mobile` | `< 640px` | Default (mobile-first) |\n| `tablet` | `≥ 768px` | Tablet |\n| `desktop` | `≥ 1024px` | Desktop |\n| `wide` | `≥ 1440px` | Wide |\n\n### 5.2 Layout Adaptations by Breakpoint\n\n#### Mobile (`< 640px`)\n\n```\nAddEditBookmarkPage:\n  padding: 24px 16px\n\nFormContainer:\n  max-width: 100%         ← no card framing needed; flush to padding\n  padding: 24px 16px      ← reduced inner padding\n  border-radius: 8px      ← small, since near viewport edge\n  box-shadow: none        ← optional: elevation suppressed at narrow width\n\nFormActions:\n  flex-direction: column  ← stack Save above Cancel\n  gap: 12px\n\nSaveButton, CancelButton:\n  width: 100%             ← full-width buttons on mobile\n\nPageHeader:\n  gap: 8px\n  PageTitle font-size: 20px (heading-3 scale as fallback)\n```\n\n#### Tablet (`≥ 768px`)\n\n```\nAddEditBookmarkPage:\n  padding: 48px 32px\n\nFormContainer:\n  max-width: 480px        ← centered column kicks in\n  padding: 32px\n  border-radius: 12px (medium)\n  box-shadow: elevation.level-1 (card appears)\n\nFormActions:\n  flex-direction: row     ← inline Save + Cancel\n  justify-content: flex-start\n\nSaveButton, CancelButton:\n  width: auto             ← natural/content width\n```\n\n#### Desktop (`≥ 1024px`) and Wide (`≥ 1440px`)\n\n```\nAddEditBookmarkPage:\n  padding: 64px 48px      ← more breathing room\n\nFormContainer:\n  max-width: 480px        ← unchanged; form width is capped\n  Centered via align-items: center on parent\n\n(No other structural changes — form is already optimally"
}